## 🎛️ Motherboard

### What is a Motherboard?

The **motherboard** is the nervous system of your computer - a printed circuit board (PCB) that connects all hardware components together.

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              MOTHERBOARD LAYOUT                      │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                      │
│   ┌─────────┐      ┌──────────┐                    │
│   │   CPU   │      │  RAM     │                    │
│   │ Socket  │      │ Slots    │                    │
│   └────┬────┘      └────┬─────┘                    │
│        │                │                          │
│   ┌────┴────────────────┴─────────────────┐        │
│   │    Northbridge / PCH (Platform        │        │
│   │    Controller Hub)                    │        │
│   └────┬─────────────────────────────┬────┘        │
│        │                             │             │
│   ┌────▼─────┐  ┌────────────┐  ┌──▼───────┐    │
│   │   GPU    │  │ Storage    │  │ Network  │    │
│   │ Slots    │  │ Controller │  │ Card     │    │
│   └──────────┘  └────────────┘  └──────────┘    │
│                                                      │
│   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│   │  Southbridge / I/O Controller              │  │
│   │  (USB, Audio, SATA, etc.)                  │  │
│   └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                      │
│   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│   │  BIOS/UEFI ROM                             │  │
│   │  (Firmware)                                │  │
│   └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Key Motherboard Components

| Component | Function |
|-----------|----------|
| **Socket** | Holds the CPU |
| **Chipset** | Controls communication between CPU, RAM, and other components |
| **Power Connectors** | Supplies power to all components |
| **BIOS/UEFI** | Firmware that initializes hardware during startup |
| **PCIe Slots** | For graphics cards, sound cards, network cards |
| **SATA Ports** | For connecting hard drives and SSDs |

