│ NVMe SSD         3000-5000 MB/s  ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓   │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Real-world Impact:
- HDD:       Boot time ~60-90 seconds
- SATA SSD:  Boot time ~30-45 seconds
- NVMe SSD:  Boot time ~10-15 seconds
