**Software** is everything you see on your screen - the visual, interactive layer of computing.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│         SOFTWARE CATEGORIES                 │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                              │
│  1️⃣  OPERATING SYSTEMS                       │
│     └─ Windows, macOS, Linux, iOS, Android  │
│                                              │
