## 🎯 Key Takeaways

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  REMEMBER THIS:                              │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                              │
│  🧠 CPU = Brain (Processes instructions)   │
│  💾 RAM = Short-term memory (Fast, volatile)│
│  🗄️  HDD/SSD = Long-term memory (Slow,      │
│      non-volatile)                          │
│  ⚙️  Motherboard = Nervous system (connects)│
│  ⚡ Firmware = Bridge (initializes system) │
│                                              │
│  When you use your computer:                │
│  1. CPU fetches data from RAM               │
│  2. Processes using ALU & Registers         │
│  3. Stores results back to RAM              │
│  4. GPU displays results on screen          │
│  5. When you save, data goes to HDD/SSD    │
│                                              │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

