│                                                       │
│  👨‍🍳 Chef (CPU)                                       │
│     └─ Reads recipe (fetches)                        │
│        Understands instructions (decodes)            │
│        Performs cooking (executes)                   │
│                                                       │
│  📝 Notepad (Registers)                              │
│     └─ Chef's scratchpad for quick notes             │
│        Super fast but limited space                  │
│                                                       │
│  🧠 Memory (Cache)                                   │
│     └─ Chef remembers frequently used steps          │
│        Faster than looking at recipe                 │
│                                                       │
│  🍽️  Served Dish (Output)                            │
│     └─ Final result shown to you                     │
